    "\", p.2 2 Ante [111] Origination & issuance \"On the one hand, the market for decentralized finance (DeFi) is constantly producing new mechanisms, such as initial exchange offerings (IEOs), initial dex offerings (IDOs) or security token offerings (STOs)\", p.1325 3 Ante, Fiedler [112] Deposits & loans \"An analysis of decentralized markets and their fully transparent life cycles could provide deeper insights into the actual benefits of stablecoins, which, besides trading, include their use as a non-volatile safe haven, a means for unwinding arbitrage and their use in DeFi to access loans or other financial products."
